title: You Decide If The Winners Win, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO45
description: There is a conflict going on in America, a great war for the heart of the nation. But it's not between the Democrats and Republicans, the far right and the far left, or traditionalists vs. progressives.  It's between those who promote the culture of winning and those who want the country to slide into excuse-making and laziness.  Who will win this battle?  It's up to you to decide.
